beer.beer_description:
Crafted with Belgian specialty yeast. Medium bodied pouring a rich golden orange hue. 
Moderate malty, biscuity flavour with a backbone of spice derived from a healthy percentage of Rye malt. Aroma of passion fruit, melon, stone fruit, balanced with a low peppery, floral, woody phenols. Welcome to Belgium.
